      <h2 style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px); font-weight: 700; color: #1C1C1E; line-height: 1.25; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">What do buyers ask about living in Knutsford?</h2>
      <p style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #444444; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">Knutsford buyers most frequently ask about house prices, commute times, school options, and brine subsidence risk. The seven questions below cover the due diligence points that consistently arise during WA16 property searches.</p>
